The '''Salinrerian Sea''' was presumably located on [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]]. [[Slaag Lado]] a [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[Draag]] created a seismic shock pulse in the sea. This created a rift, causing large amounts of environmental damage and perpetual rain. For this Slaag had a price on his own head which was claimed by [[Jango Fett/Legends|Jango Fett]].

